    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Add the ability to pass an INI string to Zend_Config_Ini and have it parse the string.</p>

<p>At present, it is not possible to parse an INI string via Zend_Config_Ini. The string must be written to a file first.</p>

